{"tid":46564,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，盲撐肥婆icon都係高登派黎嘅打手","createTime":"2016-12-19T17:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T18:57:41.000Z","uid":34771,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5375931214d58d19104939732d91bfbd9d9f43","tid":46564,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:55:57.000Z","msg":"1 set icon靚唔靚好主觀<br />\n所以暫時唔評論<br />\n<br />\n但係支持呢種管理論壇方式,就一定係唔尊重民主自由嘅表現 依班打手根本就想將連登admin改寫成新嘅林祖舜 <br />\n甚至有打手話唔出聲反對就=支持，立場中立就=支持 真係好恐怖<br />\n佢哋有咩居心 大家心知肚明<br />\n<br />\n今次admin冇開公告或公投俾會員參與，已經係漠視民意<br />\n如果當今次係冇事發生過，你諗下你同林祖舜有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n另外，已經有巴打開左公投post <br />\n現時係大部分巴打反對肥婆icon上架<br />\n希望admin可以正視呢個問題"},{"pid":"ef6439f1873e58903f48eea0fe1f7bd0b1392510","tid":46564,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"a4fc52514b3444d94506b47f96e9b1f4a0375568","tid":46564,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c61fe817591d3e96634f11e8d887dfe47cbb32d6","tid":46564,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29d0dbf9e99de61d263dcd75398d5d0f2309e66e","tid":46564,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:57:30.000Z","msg":"同意公投決定"},{"pid":"a0607c35dc8e66d58d2df96df194304c187c995f","tid":46564,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:59:36.000Z","msg":"留意到打手唔敢入呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e534a79efe6e5a291c232dc9fc54b03d589fa8","tid":46564,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"又係呢種無限上綱上線拉高登落水post#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"7336b320cc72a660e3b5341aa6631f1a6a9d402f","tid":46564,"uid":12376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"班濕鳩肥婆icon打手啲理由黎黎去去就係：<br />\n1. 好俾心機整<br />\n      偷換慨念：俾心機=適合=要支持？<br />\n2. 有個圍爐post 「公投」過<br />\n       Assume 全部人都入過去投票/ 投票結果代表全部人<br />\n3. 唔中意咪唔好用/番高登/自己開新壇<br />\n       梨吾中意米吾巧用羅=3=典解吊禾咼T_T<br />\n<br />\n然後無視 set icon 無共鳴、吹奏肥婆 嘅問題，再用以上「理由」+人身攻擊黎屌鳩所有反對聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c156fae6758d30a047d05930ce0f81a94114b236","tid":46564,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"打手出句聲啦"},{"pid":"43cc45992e5b290c62a065b0b0b0c6a38036309f","tid":46564,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:29:27.000Z","msg":"唔講icon問題<br />\n我第一眼見到你個名有支那國旗就好想打撚柒你先"},{"pid":"68e1cfcbf22eeac589afdb8f8c474213081b5f21","tid":46564,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講icon問題<br />\n我第一眼見到你個名有支那國旗就好想打撚柒你先</blockquote><br />\nit is 中超"}]}